{"tid":1472100,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉天水圍警署外放煙花襲市民    3男半個月後落網","createTime":"2019-08-14T12:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T08:07:54.000Z","uid":48093,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"cfd5d1baef88db1a9cd3de112233f85a009db5a0","tid":1472100,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190814/large/1565785981_20e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190814%2Flarge%2F1565785981_20e4.jpg&h=e7502f6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方上月30日在天水圍「連儂牆」處理一宗襲擊及刑毀案時，疑執法偏頗引起巿民不滿，數百人包圍天水圍警署要求警方交代，其間一輛套假車牌的黑色私家車駛至，向群眾直接發射多枚「穿雲箭」煙花施襲，事件釀成至少6人受傷。有網民形容事件是恐怖襲擊，懷疑與區內鄉黑勢力有關，至今日警方於元朗區拘捕一名27歲姓邱本地男子，一名34歲姓陳本地男子及一名26歲姓郭本地男子涉嫌「非法燃放煙花爆竹」及「行使虛假文書」，3名被捕男子現正被扣留調查。"},{"pid":"01f3e11f652d0caec99eb092607f9e48e10c4f85","tid":1472100,"uid":196924,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:56:48.000Z","msg":"咁都冇企圖謀殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48a2528aeb5b18ae4f83349f473c2d81700aa8c","tid":1472100,"uid":74155,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:58:21.000Z","msg":"屌以為係啲咩大鑊嘢<br />\n非法放煙花<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b7ea44108dae07f0dcb0da275ebecbff15e98d","tid":1472100,"uid":214662,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:58:47.000Z","msg":"想問下 黑警哥哥 幾時唔起訴 放人呀？"},{"pid":"ee162d0d2f6cdd088f1fc2ed387f7e1ec4e143e2","tid":1472100,"uid":27432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:00:01.000Z","msg":"wa 好撚快手WO 屌你，<br />\n啲狗唔洗啦？無一個有錯？<br />\n唔洗旨意市民會原諒你地呀黑警！"},{"pid":"06332bf9ec69e4ec8a9a61eba54782f6267b8051","tid":1472100,"uid":247184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:02:15.000Z","msg":"哦，轉頭未又係罪錢當無數"},{"pid":"6726b235575a3ef3f706370c835996b6924